{
  "stem": "9245.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they killed the Germans, and they took away their food, like grains, and all kinds of food that you could store, and brought it into the forest.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is how they-- they acted as a regular piece of army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is how they assisted the front lines in fighting the Germans, by doing damage in the back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so, since they said that they're taking anybody, girls, boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my sister and I joined, and they took into one brigade that dealt specifically with doing all the cooking and all the sewing and all the-- the man-- mending clothing, you know, for the-- for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- you dealt with 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were doing all these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like-- like living on a farm, cooking for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You needed three meals a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then there were also-- while they were doing all their activities by you know, doing all the fighting with the Germans and killing, they had wounded.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they brought the wounded, and you had to tend to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was ser-- they put me in charge, like I was a nurse, and I was tending the wounded.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and in the meantime, because of the unsanitary conditions-- don't forget that we're living in the same clothes, no bath, no change, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just slept in the same clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept in the forest or sometimes in a village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the sanitary conditions were horrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were afflicted with a tremendous amount of lice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these lice were carrying diseases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there-- there was an outbreak of typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was-- I was tending to the sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, my sin-- my sister was a seamstress.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
